HEADWORD: Glandiform
<hw>Gland"i*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>glans</ets>, <ets>glandis</ets>, acorn + <ets>-form</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>glandiforme</ets> .]</ety> <def>Having the form of a gland or nut;
resembling a gland.</def>⟦br⟧
